page.title: 09MY SELF
page.content:
I am Kris Langmead.I am 11 years old and live at 84,Gould Road,Barnstaple.I have a little sister called Caren aged 5.My favourite things are Badge Collecting and helping my Dad mend Cars.I have 2 bicycles,a train set as big as a room and seven trains.My Dad has a car called a fiat 132 ss bertini.My favourite programs are the A team,Knight Rider,Hardcastle and McCormick.I do not understad anything about pollitics because I'm not an adult and even some of the adults I know do not understand either.My favourite subject at school is maths.
By Kris Langmead
